%pgx
cs = g.createChangeSet()
rs = g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT p, i.amount
  MATCH (p)-[:has_income]->(i)
""")
for (r in rs) {
  v = r.getVertex(1)
  i = r.getDouble(2)
  cs.updateVertex(v.getId()).setProperty("tax_income", i * 0.05)
}
g = cs.build()
g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT p.name, p.tax_income
  MATCH (p)
  WHERE p.type = 'Person'
""")

paragraphs.text:
%pgx
cs = g.createChangeSet()
rs = g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT p, p.tax_income, p.tax_car, p.tax_house
  MATCH (p)
  WHERE p.type = 'Person'
""")
for (r in rs) {
  v = r.getVertex(1)
  t = r.getLong(2) + r.getLong(3) + r.getLong(4)
  cs.updateVertex(v.getId()).setProperty("tax_total", t)
}
g = cs.build()
rs = g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT ID(p), p.tax_income, p.tax_car, p.tax_house, p.tax_total, p.tax_paid
  MATCH (p)
  WHERE p.type = 'Person'
""")

%md
## ML Training Input

%pgx
g.queryPgql("""
  SELECT
    ID(p)                    AS person_id
  , p.name                   AS name
  , p.tax_income             AS tax_income
  , p.tax_car                AS tax_car
  , p.tax_house              AS tax_house
  , p.tax_total              AS tax_total
  , p.tax_paid               AS tax_paid
  , p.tax_total - p.tax_paid AS tax_unpaid
  , p.family_house           AS family_house
  , p.expensive_school       AS expensive_school
  , p.foreign_account        AS foreign_account
  MATCH (p)
  WHERE p.type = 'Person'
""")
